3DGS Editor License Notice
==========================

Language / 语言 / 言語: [English](#english) | [中文](#中文) | [日本語](#日本語)

Important: The English license text is the authoritative version. The Chinese
and Japanese sections are non-authoritative translations and explanations for
reader convenience.

